title: Sample Book, "Documentaire French Classical Imports, Volume II", 1965–67
creditline: Gift of The Museum at The Fashion Institute of Technology
description: Documentary collection of French-inspired designs including paisley, toile, Chinoiserie and crewel designs. Each design shown in mulitple colorways. Matching fabric swatches included. Color photograph shows wallpaper in situ.
